						%h2 upcoming events
						%h3 Tuesday, June 18th, 2013 -- Hershey Anti-BSL Group: 
						%p Hershey’s Anti-BSL Group is a non-profit Ontario based “grassroots” initiative aimed at removing Breed Specific Legislation (BSL) through public awareness, education and political activism while promoting responsible dog ownership. Their mandate is to restore fair and equal treatment for all dog owners. Find out more about them here, <a href="http://supporthersheysbill.com/">Support Hersheys Bill</a>

						%h2 recent events
						%h3 April 23rd, 2013 - Heavenly Hills Animal Santuary
						%p Giving abused and abandoned animals a second chance at happiness and a home in Lucan, Ontario. Check out their facebook page <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Heavenly-Hills-Animal-Sanctuary/326431814149324">here</a>.

						%h3 February 26th, 2013 - Ruby Ranch Pig Sanctuary
						%p Ruby Ranch, a small family run mission near Arthur, Ontario, is a sanctuary strictly for pigs who have been discarded or forgotten by petting zoos and negligent owners. Read more about the sanctuary <a href="http://www.rubyranch.ca/">here</a>.

						%h3 November 6th, 2012 - Teja's Animal Refuge
						%p For 23 years Nicole Joncas, now 67, has been running Teja's Animal Refuge. It has been home to hundreds of abused and abandonned animals of all shapes and sizes. Check out her website <a href="http://tejasanimalrefuge.ca/">here</a>.

						%h3 Check out our <a class="bottom-link" href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Sadies-Diner-And-Juice-Bar/221474964545386">Facebook Page</a> to see all past & upcoming events at Sadie's Diner!
					%aside
						.chili-explanation
							%h3.title What is Chili-for-Charity?
							%p On a bi-monthly basis, Sadie's Diner presents Chili-for-Charity: a night where all proceeds go towards a worthy local cause.
							%p A suggested donation of $10 gets you all-you-can-eat vegan chili (served with chips).
							%p Please send any inquiries/charity recommendations to: <a href="mailto:info@sadiesdiner.com"> info@sadiesdiner.com</a>
